@@ -1,13 +0,0 @@
----
-"@mcpjam/inspector": minor
-"@mcpjam/sdk": minor
-"@mcpjam/cli": minor
----
-
-Release the latest computer environments, host compatibility, harness, skills, and playground updates.
-
-- Add computer environments across Inspector and the CLI, including `mcpjam env` commands, hosted environment selection, run-detail surfacing, and eval sandbox support.
-- Add host compatibility platform operations and CLI checks, plus SDK market-host profiles, capability presets, widget-usage scanning, and host connection helpers.
-- Add Claude Code and Codex harness support with capability-driven built-in tools and runtime skill handling.
-- Add hosted Cloud Skills support through project Computers, including server APIs, UI picker integration, and synthetic session execution.
-- Improve Playground and Tools workflows with inline tool result editing, copy-all actions, and host-scoped command execution.
